commit b834150fe57596f1828c6f13bc509ac718c38dae
Author: MichelKerkmeester <82775228+MichelKerkmeester@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 4 13:49:35 2026 +0200

    feat(mcp-server): opt-in similarity + supersession relation inference (026/023)
    
    Adds the two collectors packet 021 deferred to backfillRelationInference, both opt-in (default off): similarity 'supports' from the cached memory_index.related_memories column (threshold>=75, top-K<=5, no live vector scan) and 'contradicts' from memory_lineage.superseded_by_memory_id. Both inherit dryRun-default + created_by='auto' guards (strength<=0.5, per-node cap, idempotent); graceful no-op on absent schema. Wired through schema/types/handler with deterministic, sqlite-vec-free tests.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

