commit d32d90c3f15be018dea60ba615771ffb5a67e193
Author: MichelKerkmeester <82775228+MichelKerkmeester@users.noreply.github.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 4 12:59:17 2026 +0200

    feat(mcp-server): bounded dryRun-default relation-inference backfill (026/021)
    
    Builds the real relation-inference backfill behind packet 019's honest stat: infers typed created_by='auto' causal edges from existing deterministic signals (spec-document chains + lineage predecessor links), default dryRun, bounded limit (<=2000), transactional, idempotent, and invalidates the entity-density cache after writes.
    
    Flips backfillJob.implemented to true with a callable command wired onto memory_causal_stats({ backfill }); no new MCP tool. Refreshes the causal README and tool-layer dispatch type.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

